4% assumable FHA Loan. Home has a large open kitchen to family room with serve bar that seats 4 easily. C-tile in entry, kitchen, nook, baths and utility room. Stainless steel appliances - dishwasher, microwave, slide in electric range cooktop. Upstairs Game Room is very large and makes for a perfect child's play room, Game Room or Man cave. Very nice covered patio

Please connect with Todd Gibbons with all question regarding this property information below
